{"tid":418077,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"亂放生釀生態災難　「科學怪魚」襲加國","createTime":"2017-09-29T09:05:59.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-29T19:50:45.000Z","uid":22675,"like":6,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"e4528c19172fbfb1135f50159e27f209331327f7","tid":418077,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-29T09:05:59.000Z","msg":"09月29日(五) 12:46   <br />\n<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/int/bkn/cnt/news/20170929/mobile/bknint-20170929124625275-0929_17011_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fint%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20170929%2Fmobile%2Fbknint-20170929124625275-0929_17011_001.html&d=lbtpjeH8lVj6cnSWx67hK8P%2FddU7lKBqZb2OVh9Tir8%3D&h=b80f80fe\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/int/bkn/cnt/news/20170929/mobile/bknint-20170929124625275-0929_17011_001.html</a><br />\n<br />\n隨便放生物種，可能會導致生態災難。加拿大艾伯塔省聖艾伯特市近年便慘遭數以千計的「科學怪魚」侵襲，牠們不但無懼水塘乾涸，甚至連電擊也不怕，令當地政府十分擔心。<br />\n<br />\n官員表示，相信早於數年前有人將一些亞洲金魚（Asian goldfish）在一個池塘放生，結果牠們繁殖了數以千計的後代，並佔領整個池塘。由於亞洲金魚適應力強，而且非常強壯，危害當地的原生物種數量。 <br />\n<br />\n環境主管康斯魯德（Leah Kongsrude）表示：「在魚缸內，牠們也許看來很可愛，但一旦把牠們放到自然世界，牠們就可長成『科學怪魚』。」當局一直努力清除牠們，包括嘗試抽走池塘的水，令池塘在冬天結冰，又試過電擊池塘，不過這些金魚成功「捱過」。金魚現時蔓延到另一個池塘，當局終決定下月在2個池塘投放化學品，殺滅金魚。"},{"pid":"31722f31931c5f5408af4ad6e330905217b7b056","tid":418077,"uid":68689,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-29T09:07:03.000Z","msg":"同中國人講有野食啦"},{"pid":"0d1e13a42497a364c8713adfbb3a77f09c656630","tid":418077,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-29T09:18:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"96cd1e7575d7ec48472403fa97ad1f72eb935e3d","tid":418077,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-29T09:53:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"afb434430cb0a246e472e2fee4abec7aa1208c3d","tid":418077,"uid":49588,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime"